Well, yeah, yeah. And that I think we do in the I think there's two ways. So like, the focus that

00:44:16.459 --> 00:44:21.659
we have on creating data products, and not just data products that are static, but like

00:44:21.659 --> 00:44:26.219
shiny applications, or scheduled, you know, reports that you can parameterize reports that

00:44:26.219 --> 00:44:33.020
you can schedule. That is a way to take the expertise, knowledge, and skills of data scientists

00:44:33.020 --> 00:44:38.939
